<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Performance Review</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .review-type-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .review-info {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .due-date-highlight {
            color: #EF4444;
        }
        .what-to-expect {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .what-to-expect h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .what-to-expect ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .what-to-expect li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .deadline-notice {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border: 1px solid #F59E0B;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Performance Review</h1>
            <div><span class="review-type-badge">{{reviewType}}</span></div>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>Your <strong>{{reviewType}}</strong> performance review for the <strong>{{reviewCycle}}</strong> cycle is now open. This is an opportunity to reflect on your accomplishments, set goals, and have a meaningful conversation with your manager.</p>

            <div class="review-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Review Cycle:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{reviewCycle}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Review Type:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{reviewType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Submission Deadline:</span>
                    <span class="info-value due-date-highlight">{{dueDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="what-to-expect">
                <h3>What to include in your self-assessment:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Key achievements and contributions during this cycle</li>
                    <li>Challenges faced and how you addressed them</li>
                    <li>Skills developed and areas of improvement</li>
                    <li>Goals you would like to set for the next cycle</li>
                    <li>Any support or resources you need from your manager</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="deadline-notice">
                <strong>Deadline:</strong> Please complete your self-assessment by <strong>{{dueDate}}</strong>. Submissions after the deadline may not be included in this review cycle.
            </div>

            <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="cta-button">Start Performance Review</a>

            <p>If you have any questions about the review process, please reach out to your manager or the HR team.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
